New Delhi, the 18th May, 2007
28 Vaisakha, 1929 (S)
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 18th May,
2007, Smt. V. Radhika Selvi assumed the charge of the office of the Minister
of State in the Ministry of Home Affairs.
(K.L. Sharma)
